                                }
                                .features-section { background-color: #f9f8f6; padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
                                .features-section .section-intro { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #6b7280; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75; }
                                .feature-card { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #fbfaf8 100%); border-radius: 1.1rem; padding: 1.6rem; height: 100%; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.08); transition: box-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease; border: 1px solid #eeece8; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
                                .feature-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 16px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12); transform: translateY(-3px); }
                                .feature-icon-wrap { width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 0.9rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(238, 121, 19, 0.14), rgba(147, 176, 35, 0.2)); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(238, 121, 19, 0.12); }
                                .feature-icon-wrap .fas, .feature-icon-wrap .fa { color: var(--qwc-orange); font-size: 1.15rem; }
                                .feature-link-title { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 0.72rem 1rem; border-radius: 999px; background: var(--qwc-soft); color: var(--qwc-green-deep); font-size: 0.96rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.01em; text-decoration: none; transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(88, 150, 50, 0.18); }
                                .feature-card .card-desc { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 0; }
                                .feature-link { margin-top: auto; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 0.72rem 1rem; border-radius: 999px; background: #1f2937; color: #ffffff; font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; transition: background-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease; }
                                .feature-link-title:hover,
                                .feature-link:hover { background: var(--qwc-green); color: #ffffff; transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(88, 150, 50, 0.18); }
                                .capability-section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
                                .capability-section.is-tinted { background-color: #f4f2ef; }
                                .capability-intro { max-width: 760px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
                                .capability-kicker { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: var(--qwc-soft); color: var(--qwc-green-deep); font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.03em; text-decoration: none; padding: 0.5rem 0.9rem; border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 0.85rem; box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(88, 150, 50, 0.16); transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease; }
                                .capability-kicker:hover { background: var(--qwc-green); color: #ffffff; transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(88, 150, 50, 0.16); }
                                .capability-title { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.25; margin-bottom: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
                                .capability-desc { color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.98rem; line-height: 1.75; }
                                .capability-card { position: relative; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #fcfbf9 100%); border: 1px solid #ece8e1; border-radius: 1.3rem; overflow: hidden; min-height: 380px; height: 100%; box-shadow: 0 12px 34px rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.08); }
                                .capability-card-image { position: absolute; top: 1.2rem; left: 1.2rem; bottom: 1.2rem; width: 56%; min-width: 360px; max-width: 620px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #edf3f6 0%, #e3ecef 100%); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 1.35rem; border-radius: 1.1rem; box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(19,35,33,0.04); }
                                .capability-card-image img { display: block; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain; object-position: center; }
                                .capability-card-body { min-height: 380px; margin-left: 58%; padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem 1.4rem 0.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-start; }
                                .capability-card-title { position: absolute; top: 1.75rem; left: 1.75rem; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 0.56rem 0.95rem; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(68, 117, 40, 0.94); color: #ffffff; font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0; letter-spacing: -0.01em; box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(68, 117, 40, 0.22); z-index: 3; backdrop-filter: blur(6px); }
                                .capability-card-text { color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.93rem; line-height: 1.72; max-width: 26rem; }
                                .capability-card-labels { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.55rem; margin-top: 0.95rem; }
                                .capability-card-label { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 0.42rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 999px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(238, 121, 19, 0.1), rgba(147, 176, 35, 0.14)); color: #44622f; font-size: 0.84rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(88, 150, 50, 0.14); white-space: nowrap; }
                                .capability-section .columns.is-variable.is-5 { margin-top: 0.5rem; row-gap: 1rem; }
                                .capability-section .columns.is-variable.is-5 > .column { flex: 0 0 100%; width: 100%; max-width: 100%; }
                                .arch-card { transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease; }
                                .arch-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.10) !important; }
                                .section-eyebrow { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(238, 121, 19, 0.12), rgba(147, 176, 35, 0.16)); color: var(--qwc-green); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.3rem 0.85rem; border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 1rem; box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(88, 150, 50, 0.16); }
                                .section-main-title { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #1f2937; letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1.25; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
                                @media (max-width: 768px) { .section-main-title, .capability-title { font-size: 1.6rem; } .capability-card { min-height: auto; } .capability-card-image { position: static; width: auto; min-width: 0; max-width: none; min-height: 240px; height: 240px; margin: 0 1.2rem 1rem 1.2rem; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 1rem; } .capability-card-body { min-height: auto; margin-left: 0; padding: 1.2rem 1.2rem 1.2rem 1.2rem; justify-content: flex-start; } .capability-card-title { top: 1.2rem; left: 1.2rem; } .capability-card-text { max-width: none; } .capability-section .columns.is-variable.is-5 > .column { flex: 0 0 100%; width: 100%; max-width: 100%; } }

                            section(class="features-section", id="core-capabilities")
                                div(class="container")
                                    div(class="has-text-centered mb-6")
                                        span(class="section-eyebrow") Capabilities
                                        h2(class="section-main-title") Powerful Web GIS Capabilities
                                        p(class="section-intro") Explore, analyze and manage geospatial data directly in your browser with a flexible and extensible web GIS platform.

                                    div(class="columns is-multiline is-variable is-5 mt-5")
                                        div(class="column is-4-desktop is-6-tablet is-12-mobile")
                                            div(class="feature-card")
                                                div(class="feature-icon-wrap")
                                                    i(class="fas fa-map-marked-alt")
                                                a(class="feature-link-title", href="#map-visualization") Core Map Experience
                                                div(class="card-desc") Manage layers, search data, inspect features, and share map context through one cohesive GIS interface.

                                        div(class="column is-4-desktop is-6-tablet is-12-mobile")
                                            div(class="feature-card")
                                                div(class="feature-icon-wrap")
                                                    i(class="fas fa-chart-line")
                                                a(class="feature-link-title", href="#data-analysis") Data Interaction & Editing
                                                div(class="card-desc") Draw, edit, measure, export, print, and work with structured attribute data through configurable editing workflows.

                                        div(class="column is-4-desktop is-6-tablet is-12-mobile")
                                            div(class="feature-card")
                                                div(class="feature-icon-wrap")
                                                    i(class="fas fa-search")
                                                a(class="feature-link-title", href="#search-discovery") Analysis & Advanced Tools
