                                        div(class="column is-4-desktop is-6-tablet is-12-mobile")
                                            div(class="feature-card")
                                                div(class="feature-icon-wrap")
                                                    i(class="fas fa-plug")
                                                a(class="feature-link-title", href="#integration-interoperability") Integration & Architecture
                                                div(class="card-desc") Build on QGIS Server, microservices, admin tooling, and APIs to integrate QWC into larger technical environments.

