                                            div(class="feature-card")
                                                div(class="feature-icon-wrap")
                                                    i(class="fas fa-user-shield")
                                                a(class="feature-link-title", href="#administration-security") Security & User Management
                                                div(class="card-desc") Control authentication, permissions, configuration, theming, accessibility, and user preferences across deployments.

