                                            div(class="feature-card")
                                                div(class="feature-icon-wrap")
                                                    i(class="fas fa-cubes")
                                                a(class="feature-link-title", href="#platform-lifecycle") Deployment, Extensibility & Ecosystem
                                                div(class="card-desc") Deploy with containers, extend through plugins, integrate mobile and offline workflows, and rely on the open source ecosystem.

